data.description: MUST SEE — This spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is conveniently located off of Northgate Road in Northgate Village Subdivision, close to Barksdale AFB. This home has been well maintained and boasts many updates throughout. New tile in bathrooms installed in 2020. New Carpets installed in bedrooms in 2023. The roof was just replaced in February 2023. Freshly painted interior and exterior. Being sold As-Is.
